    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: January 30, 2026</p>

    <p>This Privacy Policy describes our policies and procedures on the collection, use, and disclosure of your information when you use the <strong>UniTask</strong> application and tells you about your privacy rights.</p>

    <h2>1. Information Collection and Use</h2>
    <p>While using our Application, we may collect certain information to provide and improve the Service:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Data:</strong> We may collect your email address if you use Firebase Authentication to sync your tasks.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information such as your device's Internet Protocol address (e.g., IP address), device type, and app version may be collected automatically via Firebase Services.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>The app does use third-party services that may collect information used to identify you:</p>
