    </ul>

    <h2>3. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We will retain your Personal Data only for as long as is necessary for the purposes set out in this Privacy Policy, specifically for maintaining your academic tasks and account preferences.</p>

    <h2>4. Security of Your Data</h2>
    <p>The security of your data is important to us, but remember that no method of transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage is 100% secure. We strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your Personal Data.</p>

    <h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>Our Service does not address anyone under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from anyone under the age of 13.</p>

